                              Command : BESTPATH

NAME
   bestpath - Show the best path from one sector to another

Level: Expert

SYNTAX
   [##:##] Command : bestpath <SECTS> <SECTS>

The  bestpath  command  shows you the best path from any sector to any sector.
You must own both sectors.

The path shown by bestpath is the cheapest owned existing  path  in  terms  of
mobility.

Note  that  if  you  give these commands areas, they will show you more paths.
For example,

   [##:##] Command : bestpath #1 #2

will show the best paths from all sectors in realm 1 to  all  the  sectors  in
realm 2.

SEE ALSO
   distribute, Maps

